<template>
  <el-dialog
    :visible='instruction'
    width="50%"
    :before-close='handleClose'
  >
    
  </el-dialog>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  props: {
    instruction: {
      type: Boolean,
      default: false
    }
  },
  data() {

  },
  methods: {
    handleClose() {
      this.$emit('closeInstruction')
    }
  }
}
</script>
